

Reporting Bugs
--------------

  To report a bug please use the xen-tools mailing list:

        http://xen-tools.org/software/xen-tools/lists.html

  If you're capable of fixing it yourself a patch is appreciated,
 and a test case would be a useful bonus.


Known Bugs
----------

  The handling of multiple configuration files for the mirror setup
 is a little crazy.  It probably makes sense to setup:

                /etc/rinse/mirrors.txt

  Then inside that have:

   ..
   fedora-core-4.i386  = http://.....
   fedora-core-4.amd64 = http://.....
   ..

  etc.


